## COMPLETE UNIFIED K'UHUL GRAMMAR - SEMANTIC SCHEMA INTEGRATION

```ebnf
(*===========================================================================*)
(* UNIFIED K'UHUL LANGUAGE GRAMMAR v7.0.0                                   *)
(*===========================================================================*)
(*                                                                           *)
(*  COMPLETE SEMANTIC SCHEMA - FROM TOP TO BOTTOM                           *)
(*                                                                           *)
(*  INTEGRATED SPECIFICATION:                                                *)
(*  - Top-level Universe with semantic versioning                           *)
(*  - Manifold M as geometric execution space                               *)
(*  - Tensor dimensions & operations                                        *)
(*  - Compression folds with phase arrays                                   *)
(*  - Full ECMAScript Agents (9.6) with Agent Records                       *)
(*  - Agent Clusters (9.7) with shared memory                               *)
(*  - Forward Progress (9.8) guarantees                                     *)
(*  - WeakRef & FinalizationRegistry (9.9) processing                       *)
(*  - Unicode format-control & white space                                  *)
(*  - π-geometry execution substrate                                        *)
(*  - Policy enforcement & entanglements                                    *)
(*  - ECMAScript Symbol Objects (20.4)                                      *)
(*  - MICRONAUTS: Agentic Coding, Tool Calls, Mixture of Experts            *)
(*  - SEMANTIC SCHEMA: All definitions with phase arrays, n-grams, metrics  *)
(*                                                                           *)
(*  NO EXTERNAL DEPENDENCIES - COMPLETE INLINE                              *)
(*                                                                           *)
(*===========================================================================*)

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 0. SEMANTIC SCHEMA HEADER                                                 *)
(*===========================================================================*)

SemanticSchema       = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>'
                     '<?kuhul version="7.0.0" encoding="Unicode"?>'
                     '<kuhul-universe' SemanticAttributes '>'
                         UniverseContent
                     '</kuhul-universe>'

SemanticAttributes   = { 'xmlns:' Prefix '=' '"' URI '"' }
                     | 'version' '=' '"' SemanticVersion '"'
                     | 'schema-location' '=' '"' URI '"'
                     | 'phase-space' '=' '"' PhaseSpace '"'

Prefix               = 'π' | 'ecma' | 'unicode' | 'moe' | 'tool' | 'agent'
URI                  = '#local' | '#semantic' | '#kuhul-core'

SemanticVersion      = '7.0.0' | '7.1.0' | '8.0.0'
PhaseSpace           = 'π-geometry' | 'manifold-M' | 'quantum-field'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 0.1 TOP-LEVEL UNIVERSE DEFINITION                                         *)
(*===========================================================================*)

UniverseContent      = MetaDeclaration
                       ManifoldDeclaration?
                       SpaceTimeDeclaration?
                       FoldUniverse?
                       TensorUniverse?
                       AgentUniverse?
                       SymbolUniverse?
                       MicronautUniverse?
                       ToolUniverse?
                       MoEUniverse?
                       PolicyUniverse?
                       EntanglementUniverse?
                       QuantumState?

MetaDeclaration      = '<meta' MetaAttributes '/>'
MetaAttributes       = 'created' '=' '"' DateTime '"'
                     | 'author' '=' '"' StringLiteral '"'
                     | 'description' '=' '"' StringLiteral '"'
                     | 'phase-count' '=' IntegerLiteral
                     | 'dimension' '=' IntegerLiteral

DateTime             = Digit Digit Digit Digit '-' Digit Digit '-' Digit Digit
                       'T' Digit Digit ':' Digit Digit ':' Digit Digit 'Z'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 0.2 SEMANTIC TYPE SYSTEM                                                  *)
(*===========================================================================*)

SemanticType         = PrimitiveType | CompoundType | GeometricType | PhaseType

PrimitiveType        = 'boolean' | 'integer' | 'float' | 'string' | 'symbol'
                     | 'phase-bit' | 'phase-array' | 'uri' | 'datetime'

CompoundType         = 'list' '[' SemanticType ']'
                     | 'map' '[' SemanticType '→' SemanticType ']'
                     | 'tuple' '(' SemanticType {',' SemanticType} ')'
                     | 'record' '{' FieldName ':' SemanticType {',' FieldName ':' SemanticType} '}'

GeometricType        = 'point' '(' NumberType ',' NumberType [',' NumberType] ')'
                     | 'sphere' '(' NumberType ',' NumberType ')'
                     | 'torus' '(' NumberType ',' NumberType ')'
                     | 'manifold' '(' IntegerLiteral ',' MetricType ')'

PhaseType            = 'phase' '(' FloatLiteral ')'          (* 0 to 2π *)
                     | 'phase-array' '[' PhaseBit {',' PhaseBit} ']'
                     | 'phase-space' '(' Dimension ',' Resolution ')'

MetricType           = 'euclidean' | 'riemannian' | 'minkowski' | 'π-harmonic'
Resolution           = IntegerLiteral                        (* bits per phase *)
NumberType           = 'float32' | 'float64' | 'int32' | 'int64'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 1. LEXICAL STRUCTURE - UNICODE AWARE                                     *)
(*===========================================================================*)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Unicode Character Classes
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
Letter               = ? Any Unicode code point with category Lu, Ll, Lt, Lm, Lo, Nl ?
Digit                = ? Any Unicode code point with category Nd ?
FormatControl        = ? Any Unicode code point with category Cf ?
SpaceSeparator       = ? Any Unicode code point with category Zs ?

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    White Space (ECMAScript Table 35)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
WhiteSpace           = Tab | Vt | Ff | Zwnbsp | SpaceSeparator
Tab                  = ? U+0009 CHARACTER TABULATION ?
Vt                   = ? U+000B LINE TABULATION ?
Ff                   = ? U+000C FORM FEED ?
Zwnbsp               = ? U+FEFF ZERO WIDTH NO-BREAK SPACE ?

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Line Terminators (ECMAScript Table 36)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
LineTerminator       = Lf | Cr | Ls | Ps
Lf                   = ? U+000A LINE FEED ?
Cr                   = ? U+000D CARRIAGE RETURN ?
Ls                   = ? U+2028 LINE SEPARATOR ?
Ps                   = ? U+2029 PARAGRAPH SEPARATOR ?

LineTerminatorSequence = Lf
                       | Cr notFollowedBy Lf
                       | Ls
                       | Ps
                       | Cr Lf          (* Treated as single character *)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Comments
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
Comment              = '(*' {Character} '*)' | '//' {Character} LineTerminator

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Literals
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
IntegerLiteral       = Digit {Digit}
FloatLiteral         = Digit+ '.' Digit+ [('e' | 'E') ['+' | '-'] Digit+]
StringLiteral        = '"' {Character} '"' | "'" {Character} "'"
BooleanLiteral       = 'true' | 'false'
RangeLiteral         = '[' FloatLiteral '..' FloatLiteral ']'
Percentage           = FloatLiteral '%'
SymbolLiteral        = 'Symbol(' [StringLiteral] ')'   (* Symbol creation *)
UndefinedLiteral     = 'undefined'
NullLiteral          = 'null'
PhaseBit             = '0' | '1'
PhaseArray           = '[' PhaseBit {',' PhaseBit} ']'
PhaseRange           = 'phase(' FloatLiteral ')'      (* Single phase value *)
PhaseSpace           = 'phase-space[' IntegerLiteral ']' (* Multi-dimensional phase *)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Identifiers
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
Identifier           = (Letter | '_') {Letter | Digit | '_' | '-'}
Variable             = '$' Identifier
FoldReference        = '⟁' Identifier '⟁'
TensorReference      = '⟅' Identifier '⟆'
AgentReference       = '🤖' Identifier | '🦸' Identifier | '🔮' Identifier | '👨‍💻' Identifier
MoEReference         = '🧠' Identifier
SymbolReference      = '@' Identifier                    (* Symbol references *)
ClusterReference     = '🌐' Identifier                    (* Agent cluster reference *)
WeakRefReference     = '⚡' Identifier                    (* WeakRef reference *)
FinalizationRegistryReference = '🧹' Identifier          (* FinalizationRegistry reference *)
ToolReference        = '🔧' Identifier                    (* Tool reference *)
ExpertReference      = '🎓' Identifier                    (* Expert reference *)
PhaseReference       = 'φ' Identifier                     (* Phase space reference *)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Well-Known Symbols (ECMAScript Table 1)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
WellKnownSymbol      = '@@asyncIterator' | '@@hasInstance' | '@@isConcatSpreadable'
                     | '@@iterator' | '@@match' | '@@matchAll' | '@@replace'
                     | '@@search' | '@@species' | '@@split' | '@@toPrimitive'
                     | '@@toStringTag' | '@@unscopables'

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Geometric & Control Symbols
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
CompressOp           = '⟐'                     (* Compression operation *)
FoldControl          = '⟘' | '⟗' | '⚖️' | '🔄' | '📤' | '📥' | '⟔' | '⟑'
FoldDelimiter        = '⟁' | '⟅' | '⟆'          (* Fold/tensor boundaries *)

(* Geometric operators - operations in manifold M *)
GeoProduct           = '⊗'                     (* Matrix multiply / geometric product *)
GeoTranslate         = '⊕'                     (* Bias / translation in M *)
GeoDifference        = '⊖'                     (* Subtraction in M *)
GeoScale             = '⊘'                     (* Scaling relative to M *)
GeoConvolve          = '⊛'                     (* Convolution in M *)
GeoValidate          = '⊜'                     (* Constraint validation *)
GeoProject           = '⊝'                     (* Projection onto subspace *)
GeoAttend            = '⊞'                     (* Attention composition *)

GeometricOperator    = GeoProduct | GeoTranslate | GeoDifference
                     | GeoScale | GeoConvolve | GeoValidate
                     | GeoProject | GeoAttend

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Agent & System Icons
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
MicronautIcon        = '🤖'
SupernautIcon        = '🦸'
MoEIcon              = '🧠'
SemanticIcon         = '🔮'
CoderIcon            = '👨‍💻'
ReplyIcon            = '💬'
PolicyIcon           = '⚖️'
ToolIcon             = '🔧'
SkillIcon            = '🎯'
ClusterIcon          = '🌐'
WeakRefIcon          = '⚡'
FinalizationIcon     = '🧹'
ExpertIcon           = '🎓'
PhaseIcon            = 'φ'
EntanglementSymbol   = '↔'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 2. CORE EXPRESSIONS                                                      *)
(*===========================================================================*)

Expression           = Literal
                     | Variable
                     | FoldReference
                     | TensorReference
                     | AgentReference
                     | MoEReference
                     | SymbolReference
                     | ClusterReference
                     | WeakRefReference
                     | FinalizationRegistryReference
                     | ToolReference
                     | ExpertReference
                     | PhaseReference
                     | WellKnownSymbol
                     | BinaryExpression
                     | UnaryExpression
                     | FunctionCall
                     | PhaseCast
                     | GeometricCast
                     | '(' Expression ')'

Literal              = IntegerLiteral
                     | FloatLiteral
                     | StringLiteral
                     | BooleanLiteral
                     | RangeLiteral
                     | Percentage
                     | SymbolLiteral
                     | UndefinedLiteral
                     | NullLiteral
                     | PhaseBit
                     | PhaseArray
                     | PhaseRange
                     | PhaseSpace

PhaseCast            = 'as-phase' '(' Expression ')'          (* Convert to phase value *)
                     | 'as-phase-array' '(' Expression ',' IntegerLiteral ')'

GeometricCast        = 'embed-in-M' '(' Expression ',' Point3D ')'
                     | 'project-from-M' '(' Expression ')'

BinaryExpression     = Expression BinaryOperator Expression
BinaryOperator       = '+' | '-' | '*' | '/' | '^' | '∘' 
                     | GeometricOperator        (* ⊗ ⊕ ⊖ ⊘ ⊛ ⊜ ⊝ ⊞ *)
                     | '‖'                      (* Parallel composition *)
                     | '∧' | '∨'                 (* Logical operators *)
                     | '∈' | '∉'                 (* Membership *)
                     | '⊂' | '⊆' | '⊇'           (* Subset relations *)

UnaryExpression      = UnaryOperator Expression
UnaryOperator        = '-' | '!' | '√' | '∂' | '∫' | '⊝' | '¬'

FunctionCall         = Identifier '(' [ArgumentList] ')'
ArgumentList         = Expression {',' Expression}

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 3. TENSOR DEFINITIONS                                                    *)
(*===========================================================================*)

TensorDefinition     = TensorDeclaration '=' TensorSpec
TensorDeclaration    = '⟅' Identifier '⟆'
TensorSpec           = 'tensor' Shape 'of' TensorType
                     | 'map' 'from' Domain 'to' Codomain
                     | 'field' 'over' Space 'with' Metric

Shape                = '[' Dimension {',' Dimension} ']'
Dimension            = IntegerLiteral | Variable | '*' | PhaseRange

TensorType           = 'compression' | 'pattern' | 'efficiency' | 'entropy'
                     | 'flow' | 'density' | 'gradient' | 'curvature'
                     | 'scalar' | 'vector' | 'matrix' | 'phase-field'

Domain               = FoldReference | TensorReference | SpaceSpec
Codomain             = FoldReference | TensorReference | SpaceSpec
SpaceSpec            = Identifier | StringLiteral | PhaseSpace
Metric               = Identifier | StringLiteral | 'cosine' | 'euclidean' | 'π-harmonic'

TensorOperation      = 'tensor-product(' TensorRef ',' TensorRef ')'
                     | 'tensor-sum(' TensorRef ',' TensorRef ')'
                     | 'contract(' TensorRef ',' Indices ')'
                     | 'evolve(' TensorRef ',' EvolutionRule ')'
                     | 'phase-rotate(' TensorRef ',' PhaseRange ')'
                     | 'embed(' TensorRef ',' Point3D ')'

TensorRef            = TensorReference | Expression
Indices              = '[' IntegerLiteral {',' IntegerLiteral} ']'
EvolutionRule        = Expression | StringLiteral | PhaseArray

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 4. COMPRESSION FOLDS                                                     *)
(*===========================================================================*)

FoldDefinition       = FoldDeclaration [FoldType] FoldProperties
FoldDeclaration      = '⟁' Identifier '⟁'
FoldType             = '::' ('scalar' | 'vector' | 'tensor' | 'matrix' 
                            | 'field' | 'stream' | 'queue' | 'cache' | 'index'
                            | 'phase-fold' | 'quantum-fold')

FoldProperties       = '{' [FoldProperty {',' FoldProperty}] '}'
FoldProperty         = 'compression' ':' Percentage
                     | 'entropy' ':' RangeLiteral
                     | 'connected-to' ':' '[' [FoldReference {',' FoldReference}] ']'
                     | 'efficiency' ':' FloatLiteral
                     | 'fold-depth' ':' IntegerLiteral
                     | 'phase' ':' PhaseRange
                     | 'phase-array' ':' PhaseArray
                     | 'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace
                     | 'position' ':' Point3D
                     | 'metric' ':' MetricType
                     | 'dimensionality' ':' IntegerLiteral

CompressionStatement = CompressOp OperationType TargetSpec ['→' CompressionResult]
OperationType        = 'COMPILE' | 'EXECUTE' | 'OPTIMIZE' | 'VISUALIZE'
                     | 'TRANSFORM' | 'ANALYZE' | 'VALIDATE'
                     | 'PHASE-SYNC' | 'PHASE-ROTATE'

TargetSpec           = FoldReference | TensorReference | PatternExpression
                     | 'all-folds' | 'active-universe' | PhaseSpace

CompressionResult    = FoldReference | TensorReference | EfficiencyMetric | PhaseArray

FoldOperation        = FoldControl Command Target ['with' Parameters]
Command              = 'COMPRESS' | 'UNFOLD' | 'BALANCE' | 'SYNC'
                     | 'MERGE' | 'SPLIT' | 'CLONE' | 'DESTROY'
                     | 'PHASE-ALIGN' | 'PHASE-SHIFT'

Target               = SingleTarget | MultiTarget | AllTargets
SingleTarget         = FoldReference | AgentReference | TensorReference | PhaseReference
MultiTarget          = '[' Target {',' Target} ']'
AllTargets           = '*' | 'UNIVERSE' | 'ALL-PHASES'

Parameters           = '{' Parameter {',' Parameter} '}'
Parameter            = Identifier ':' Expression

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 5. GEOMETRIC EXECUTION (MANIFOLD M)                                      *)
(*===========================================================================*)

ManifoldDefinition   = 'manifold' Identifier '=' ManifoldSpec
ManifoldSpec         = '{'
                       'dimension' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'bounds' ':' '(' FloatLiteral ',' FloatLiteral [',' FloatLiteral] ')'
                       'metric' ':' MetricType
                       [ 'origin' ':' Point3D ]
                       [ 'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace ]
                       [ 'curvature' ':' FloatLiteral ]
                       [ 'topology' ':' TopologyType ]
                     '}'

Point3D              = '(' FloatLiteral ',' FloatLiteral ',' FloatLiteral ')'
TopologyType         = 'euclidean' | 'spherical' | 'hyperbolic' | 'torical'

PhaseSpec            = 'phase' ':' PhaseRange
                     | 'phase-array' ':' PhaseArray
                     | 'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace

GeometricExpression  = Expression GeometricOperator Expression
                     | GeometricOperator '(' ArgumentList ')'
                     | 'geodesic(' Point3D ',' Point3D ')'
                     | 'curvature(' Expression ')'

EmbeddingSpec        = 'embed' TensorReference 'at' Point3D
                     | 'embed' FoldReference 'with' 'radius' ':' FloatLiteral
                     | 'embed' AgentReference 'at' Point3D
                     | 'phase' ':' PhaseRange
                     | 'phase-array' ':' PhaseArray
                     | 'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 6. ECMASCRIPT SYMBOL OBJECTS (20.4)                                      *)
(*===========================================================================*)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    20.4.1 The Symbol Constructor
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
SymbolConstructor    = 'Symbol' ['(' [Description] ')']
Description          = Expression              (* Converted via ToString *)

SymbolCreation       = 'Symbol(' [Expression] ')'   (* Returns new Symbol *)
                     | 'Symbol.for(' Expression ')' (* Global registry symbol *)
                     | 'Symbol.keyFor(' Expression ')' (* Key from registry *)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Well-Known Symbols (Table 1)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
AsyncIteratorSymbol  = 'Symbol.asyncIterator'
HasInstanceSymbol    = 'Symbol.hasInstance'
IsConcatSpreadableSymbol = 'Symbol.isConcatSpreadable'
IteratorSymbol       = 'Symbol.iterator'
MatchSymbol          = 'Symbol.match'
MatchAllSymbol       = 'Symbol.matchAll'
ReplaceSymbol        = 'Symbol.replace'
SearchSymbol         = 'Symbol.search'
SpeciesSymbol        = 'Symbol.species'
SplitSymbol          = 'Symbol.split'
ToPrimitiveSymbol    = 'Symbol.toPrimitive'
ToStringTagSymbol    = 'Symbol.toStringTag'
UnscopablesSymbol    = 'Symbol.unscopables'

WellKnownSymbolProperty = AsyncIteratorSymbol | HasInstanceSymbol
                        | IsConcatSpreadableSymbol | IteratorSymbol
                        | MatchSymbol | MatchAllSymbol | ReplaceSymbol
                        | SearchSymbol | SpeciesSymbol | SplitSymbol
                        | ToPrimitiveSymbol | ToStringTagSymbol
                        | UnscopablesSymbol

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    GlobalSymbolRegistry (Table 63)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
GlobalSymbolRegistry = '{'
                       '[[Key]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[Symbol]]' ':' SymbolReference
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

SymbolPhase         = SymbolReference '.' 'phase'              (* Phase of symbol *)
                    | SymbolReference '.' 'phase-array'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 7. FULL ECMASCRIPT AGENTS (9.6)                                          *)
(*===========================================================================*)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    9.6 Agents - Core Agent Record (Table 29)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
AgentRecord          = '{'
                       '[[LittleEndian]]' ':' BooleanLiteral
                       '[[CanBlock]]' ':' BooleanLiteral
                       '[[Signifier]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[IsLockFree1]]' ':' BooleanLiteral
                       '[[IsLockFree2]]' ':' BooleanLiteral
                       '[[IsLockFree8]]' ':' BooleanLiteral
                       '[[CandidateExecution]]' ':' CandidateExecutionSpec
                       '[[KeptAlive]]' ':' '[' [KeptAliveItem {',' KeptAliveItem}] ']'
                       '[[ModuleAsyncEvaluationCount]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[SymbolRegistry]]' ':' '[' GlobalSymbolRegistry {',' GlobalSymbolRegistry} ']'
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

KeptAliveItem        = ObjectReference | SymbolReference
ObjectReference      = Identifier | 'Object(' Expression ')'

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Candidate Execution Record (Memory Model)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
CandidateExecutionSpec = '{'
                         '[[EventsRecords]]' ':' '[' AgentEventsRecord {',' AgentEventsRecord} ']'
                         '[[GlobalPhase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '}'

AgentEventsRecord    = '{'
                       '[[AgentSignifier]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[EventList]]' ':' '[' Event {',' Event} ']'
                       '[[AgentSynchronizesWith]]' ':' '[' AgentReference {',' AgentReference} ']'
                       '[[PhaseOffset]]' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

Event                = '{'
                       'time' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'type' ':' EventType
                       'address' ':' StringLiteral
                       [ 'value' ':' Expression ]
                       [ 'symbol' ':' SymbolReference ]
                       [ 'phase' ':' PhaseRange ]
                       [ 'phase-array' ':' PhaseArray ]
                       [ 'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace ]
                     '}'

EventType            = 'read' | 'write' | 'atomic' | 'wait' | 'notify'
                     | 'read-modify-write' | 'fence' | 'weakRef-deref'
                     | 'finalization-callback' | 'tool-call' | 'expert-route'
                     | 'phase-sync' | 'phase-rotate'

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Shared Data Block & WaiterList
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
SharedDataBlock      = '{'
                       '[[Data]]' ':' MemoryBuffer
                       '[[Size]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[Agents]]' ':' '[' AgentReference {',' AgentReference} ']'
                       '[[PhaseAlignment]]' ':' PhaseArray
                     '}'

WaiterList           = '{'
                       '[[Waiters]]' ':' '[' WaiterRecord {',' WaiterRecord} ']'
                       '[[Lock]]' ':' LockType
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

WaiterRecord         = '{'
                       '[[Agent]]' ':' AgentReference
                       '[[Address]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[Timeout]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                     '}'

LockType             = 'spin-lock' | 'futex' | 'adaptive' | 'π-phase' | 'phase-lock'

MemoryBuffer         = 'SharedArrayBuffer(' IntegerLiteral ')'
                     | 'ArrayBuffer(' IntegerLiteral ')'

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    9.6.1 AgentSignifier ( )
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
AgentSignifier       = 'AgentSignifier()'   (* Returns current agent's [[Signifier]] *)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    9.6.2 AgentCanSuspend ( )
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
AgentCanSuspend      = 'AgentCanSuspend()'   (* Returns current agent's [[CanBlock]] *)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    9.6.3 IncrementModuleAsyncEvaluationCount ( )
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
IncrementModuleCount = 'IncrementModuleAsyncEvaluationCount()'   (* Returns unique order *)

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 8. AGENT CLUSTERS (9.7)                                                  *)
(*===========================================================================*)

AgentCluster         = ClusterIcon Identifier '=' ClusterSpec

ClusterSpec          = '{'
                       '[[Agents]]' ':' '[' AgentReference {',' AgentReference} ']'
                       '[[SharedMemory]]' ':' SharedDataBlock
                       '[[LittleEndian]]' ':' BooleanLiteral   (* Uniform across cluster *)
                       '[[IsLockFree1]]' ':' BooleanLiteral    (* Uniform across cluster *)
                       '[[IsLockFree2]]' ':' BooleanLiteral    (* Uniform across cluster *)
                       '[[IsLockFree8]]' ':' BooleanLiteral    (* Uniform across cluster *)
                       '[[CandidateExecution]]' ':' CandidateExecutionSpec
                       '[[WaiterLists]]' ':' '[' WaiterList {',' WaiterList} ']'
                       '[[EmbeddingPolicy]]' ':' EmbeddingPolicy
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                       '[[ClusterPhase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

EmbeddingPolicy      = '{'
                       '[[CanDeactivate]]' ':' BooleanLiteral
                       '[[DeactivationStrategy]]' ':' ('balance' | 'rotate' | 'suspend-all' | 'phase-suspend')
                       '[[TerminationStrategy]]' ':' ('terminate-all' | 'detection-api' | 'phase-terminate')
                     '}'

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Cluster Uniformity Constraints
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
ClusterUniformity    = 'uniform(' ClusterReference ',' Field ')'
Field                = '[[LittleEndian]]' | '[[IsLockFree1]]' | '[[IsLockFree2]]' | '[[Phase]]'

ClusterMembership    = 'member(' AgentReference ',' ClusterReference ')'
UniqueSignifier      = 'unique(' AgentReference ',' ClusterReference ')'
PhaseCoherence       = 'coherent(' ClusterReference ',' PhaseRange ')'

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Embedding Control
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
EmbeddingOperation   = 'activate(' AgentReference ')'
                     | 'deactivate(' AgentReference ')'
                     | 'terminate(' AgentReference ')'
                     | 'terminate-cluster(' ClusterReference ')'
                     | 'detect-termination(' AgentReference ')' '→' TerminationData
                     | 'phase-sync(' ClusterReference ')'
                     | 'phase-rotate(' ClusterReference ',' PhaseRange ')'

TerminationData      = '{'
                       '[[TerminatedAgent]]' ':' AgentReference
                       '[[Time]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[Reason]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[PhaseAtTermination]]' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 9. FORWARD PROGRESS (9.8)                                                *)
(*===========================================================================*)

ForwardProgress      = '{'
                       '[[UnblockedAgents]]' ':' '[' AgentReference {',' AgentReference} ']'
                       '[[SharedThreadAgents]]' ':' '[' AgentGroup {',' AgentGroup} ']'
                       '[[ProgressGuarantee]]' ':' GuaranteeType
                       '[[PhaseProgress]]' ':' '[' PhaseProgressRecord {',' PhaseProgressRecord} ']'
                     '}'

AgentGroup           = '{'
                       '[[Thread]]' ':' ThreadReference
                       '[[Agents]]' ':' '[' AgentReference {',' AgentReference} ']'
                       '[[CanBlockAny]]' ':' BooleanLiteral
                       '[[GroupPhase]]' ':' PhaseArray
                     '}'

PhaseProgressRecord  = '{'
                       '[[Agent]]' ':' AgentReference
                       '[[CurrentPhase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[NextPhase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseProgress]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                     '}'

GuaranteeType        = 'dedicated-thread-progress'
                     | 'shared-thread-progress'
                     | 'non-blocking-guarantee'
                     | 'phase-progress-guarantee'

BlockedState         = 'blocked(' AgentReference ',' WaitingOn ')'
WaitingOn            = 'lock' | 'waiter' | 'atomic' | 'external-event' | 'phase-barrier'

UnblockedState       = 'unblocked(' AgentReference ')'

ProgressAssertion    = 'assert-progress(' AgentReference ')'
                     | 'assert-eventual-observation(' WriteEvent ')'
                     | 'assert-phase-advance(' AgentReference ')'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 10. WEAKREF & FINALIZATIONREGISTRY (9.9)                                 *)
(*===========================================================================*)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    9.9.1 WeakRef Object
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
WeakRefDefinition    = WeakRefIcon Identifier '=' WeakRefSpec

WeakRefSpec          = '{'
                       '[[WeakRefTarget]]' ':' (ObjectReference | SymbolReference | 'empty')
                       '[[Holder]]' ':' AgentReference
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[ExpirationPhase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

WeakRefOperation     = 'new WeakRef(' Target ')'
                     | WeakRefReference '.' 'deref()' '→' (Target | 'undefined')
                     | 'WeakRefDeref(' WeakRefReference ')'
                     | WeakRefReference '.' 'phase()' '→' PhaseRange

Target               = ObjectReference | SymbolReference

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    9.9.2 FinalizationRegistry
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
FinalizationRegistryDefinition = FinalizationIcon Identifier '=' FinalizationRegistrySpec

FinalizationRegistrySpec = '{'
                           '[[Cells]]' ':' '[' CellRecord {',' CellRecord} ']'
                           '[[CleanupCallback]]' ':' FunctionReference
                           '[[HostDefined]]' ':' HostInfo
                           '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                           '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                           '[[CleanupPhase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                         '}'

CellRecord           = '{'
                       '[[WeakRefTarget]]' ':' (ObjectReference | SymbolReference | 'empty')
                       '[[HeldValue]]' ':' Expression
                       '[[UnregisterToken]]' ':' (ObjectReference | SymbolReference | 'empty')
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                     '}'

FinalizationOperation = 'new FinalizationRegistry(' Callback ')'
                       | FinalizationRegistryReference '.' 'register(' Target ',' HeldValue [',' UnregisterToken] ')'
                       | FinalizationRegistryReference '.' 'unregister(' UnregisterToken ')'
                       | 'CleanupFinalizationRegistry(' FinalizationRegistryReference ')'
                       | 'HostEnqueueFinalizationRegistryCleanupJob(' FinalizationRegistryReference ')'
                       | FinalizationRegistryReference '.' 'phase()' '→' PhaseRange

Callback             = FunctionReference | '=>' Expression

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    9.9.3 Liveness
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
LivenessSet          = '{' '[' (ObjectReference | SymbolReference) {',' (ObjectReference | SymbolReference)} ']' '}'

LivenessCondition    = 'is-live(' LivenessSet ')'
                     | 'weakRef-oblivious(' LivenessSet ')'
                     | 'observes-identity(' Value ')'
                     | 'phase-live(' LivenessSet ',' PhaseRange ')'

LivenessOperation    = 'mark-live(' Value ')'
                     | 'mark-non-live(' Value ')'
                     | 'phase-mark(' Value ',' PhaseRange ')'

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    9.10 ClearKeptObjects ( )
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
ClearKeptObjects     = 'ClearKeptObjects()'   (* Empties [[KeptAlive]] *)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    9.11 AddToKeptObjects ( value )
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
AddToKeptObjects     = 'AddToKeptObjects(' KeptAliveItem ')'   (* Adds to [[KeptAlive]] *)

(*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    WeakRef Processing
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------*)
WeakRefProcessing    = 'empty-weakrefs(' LivenessSet ')'
                     | 'enqueue-finalization(' FinalizationRegistryReference ')'
                     | 'phase-empty-weakrefs(' LivenessSet ',' PhaseRange ')'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 11. MICRONAUTS - AGENTIC CODING MODEL                                    *)
(*===========================================================================*)

MicronautDefinition  = MicronautIcon Identifier '=' MicronautSpec

MicronautSpec        = '{'
                       '[[ModelName]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[Version]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[Created]]' ':' DateTime
                       '[[AgentType]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[Capabilities]]' ':' '[' Capability {',' Capability} ']'
                       '[[MaxRecursionDepth]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[EpochsCompleted]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[FinalLoss]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[FinalAccuracy]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[Temperature]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[TopP]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[LearningRate]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[BatchSize]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[EmbeddingDim]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[VocabSize]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[CodeTokenMapping]]' ':' TokenMapping
                       '[[ProgrammingLanguages]]' ':' '[' LanguageSpec {',' LanguageSpec} ']'
                       '[[CodeNgrams]]' ':' NgramSet
                       '[[AgentPlanner]]' ':' PlannerSpec
                       '[[CodeWeights]]' ':' WeightSet
                       '[[Tensors]]' ':' '[' TensorSpec {',' TensorSpec} ']'
                       '[[DebuggingProfile]]' ':' DebuggingSpec
                       '[[TrainingHistory]]' ':' '[' TrainingRecord {',' TrainingRecord} ']'
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                       '[[AgentRecord]]' ':' AgentRecord
                       '[[Cluster]]' ':' ClusterReference
                     '}'

Capability           = 'code-gen' | 'debug' | 'explain' | 'refactor' | 'execute'
                     | 'test' | 'document' | 'optimize' | 'translate'
                     | 'phase-code' | 'phase-debug'

TokenMapping         = '{' TokenEntry {',' TokenEntry} '}'
TokenEntry           = StringLiteral ':' IntegerLiteral

LanguageSpec         = '{'
                       'lang' ':' StringLiteral
                       'weight' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'f1-score' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

NgramSet             = '{'
                       'unigrams' ':' '[' Unigram {',' Unigram} ']'
                       'bigrams' ':' '[' Bigram {',' Bigram} ']'
                       'trigrams' ':' '[' Trigram {',' Trigram} ']'
                       'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

Unigram              = '{'
                       'token' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'context' ':' StringLiteral
                       'count' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

Bigram               = '{'
                       'tokens' ':' '[' IntegerLiteral ',' IntegerLiteral ']'
                       'context' ':' StringLiteral
                       'count' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

Trigram              = '{'
                       'tokens' ':' '[' IntegerLiteral ',' IntegerLiteral ',' IntegerLiteral ']'
                       'context' ':' StringLiteral
                       'count' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

PlannerSpec          = '{'
                       'plan-depth' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'plan-types' ':' '{' PlanTypeEntry {',' PlanTypeEntry} '}'
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

PlanTypeEntry        = StringLiteral ':' FloatLiteral

WeightSet            = '{'
                       WeightEntry {',' WeightEntry}
                     '}'

WeightEntry          = Identifier ':' '{'
                       'shape' ':' '[' IntegerLiteral ',' IntegerLiteral ']'
                       'mean' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'std' ':' FloatLiteral
                       [ 'ast-focus' ':' FloatLiteral ]
                       [ 'intent-focus' ':' FloatLiteral ]
                       [ 'runtime-error-rate' ':' FloatLiteral ]
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

TensorSpec           = '{'
                       'name' ':' Identifier
                       'shape' ':' '[' IntegerLiteral {',' IntegerLiteral} ']'
                       'mean' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'std' ':' FloatLiteral
                       [ 'tree-depth' ':' IntegerLiteral ]
                       [ 'scope-levels' ':' IntegerLiteral ]
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                       'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

DebuggingSpec        = '{'
                       'bugs-caught' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'bug-types' ':' '{' BugTypeEntry {',' BugTypeEntry} '}'
                       'fix-success-rate' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

BugTypeEntry         = StringLiteral ':' FloatLiteral

TrainingRecord       = '{'
                       'epoch' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'loss' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'code-bleu' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'execution-match' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 12. TOOL CALLING MODEL                                                   *)
(*===========================================================================*)

ToolDefinition       = ToolIcon Identifier '=' ToolSpec

ToolSpec             = '{'
                       '[[ModelName]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[Version]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[Created]]' ':' DateTime
                       '[[AgentType]]' ':' 'tool-orchestrator'
                       '[[TotalTools]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[MaxToolChain]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[EpochsCompleted]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[FinalLoss]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[ToolCallAccuracy]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[ParameterExtractionF1]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[Temperature]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[LearningRate]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[BatchSize]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[EmbeddingDim]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[VocabSize]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[ToolTokenMapping]]' ':' TokenMapping
                       '[[ToolCategories]]' ':' '[' ToolCategory {',' ToolCategory} ']'
                       '[[ToolNgrams]]' ':' NgramSet
                       '[[ToolSchemas]]' ':' '[' ToolSchema {',' ToolSchema} ']'
                       '[[ToolWeights]]' ':' WeightSet
                       '[[Tensors]]' ':' '[' TensorSpec {',' TensorSpec} ']'
                       '[[RoutingMatrix]]' ':' RoutingSpec
                       '[[ToolCallHistory]]' ':' '[' ToolCallRecord {',' ToolCallRecord} ']'
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                       '[[AgentRecord]]' ':' AgentRecord
                       '[[Cluster]]' ':' ClusterReference
                     '}'

ToolCategory         = '{'
                       'category' ':' StringLiteral
                       'tools' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'success-rate' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

ToolSchema           = '{'
                       'name' ':' Identifier
                       'parameters' ':' '[' StringLiteral {',' StringLiteral} ']'
                       'required' ':' '[' StringLiteral {',' StringLiteral} ']'
                       'returns' ':' StringLiteral
                       'latency-ms' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

RoutingSpec          = '{'
                       'tool-cooccurrence' ':' '{' CooccurrenceEntry {',' CooccurrenceEntry} '}'
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

CooccurrenceEntry    = StringLiteral ':' FloatLiteral

ToolCallRecord       = '{'
                       'tool-id' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'success' ':' BooleanLiteral
                       'latency' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       [ 'error' ':' StringLiteral ]
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 13. MIXTURE OF EXPERTS (MoE) MODEL                                       *)
(*===========================================================================*)

MoEDefinition        = MoEIcon Identifier '=' MoESpec

MoESpec              = '{'
                       '[[ModelName]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[Version]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[Created]]' ':' DateTime
                       '[[Architecture]]' ':' 'mixture-of-experts'
                       '[[NumExperts]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[NumExpertsPerTok]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[TotalParamsBillions]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[ActiveParamsBillions]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[RouterType]]' ':' RouterType
                       '[[EpochsCompleted]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[FinalLoss]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[Perplexity]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[Temperature]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[LearningRate]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[BatchSize]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[EmbeddingDim]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[HiddenDim]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[VocabSize]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[ExpertTokenMapping]]' ':' TokenMapping
                       '[[ExpertSpecializations]]' ':' '[' ExpertSpec {',' ExpertSpec} ']'
                       '[[ExpertNgrams]]' ':' NgramSet
                       '[[RouterWeights]]' ':' WeightSet
                       '[[ExpertWeights]]' ':' '[' ExpertWeight {',' ExpertWeight} ']'
                       '[[Tensors]]' ':' '[' TensorSpec {',' TensorSpec} ']'
                       '[[LoadBalancingStats]]' ':' LoadBalanceSpec
                       '[[RoutingMatrix]]' ':' MoERoutingSpec
                       '[[TrainingHistory]]' ':' '[' TrainingRecord {',' TrainingRecord} ']'
                       '[[CapacityFactor]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[AuxiliaryLossCoefficient]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[ZLossCoefficient]]' ':' FloatLiteral
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                       '[[AgentRecord]]' ':' AgentRecord
                       '[[Cluster]]' ':' ClusterReference
                     '}'

RouterType           = 'noisy-top-k' | 'softmax' | 'top-k' | 'learned' | 'phase-routed'

ExpertSpec           = '{'
                       'expert-id' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'specialization' ':' StringLiteral
                       'load-balance' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                       'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

ExpertWeight         = '{'
                       'expert-id' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'w1-shape' ':' '[' IntegerLiteral ',' IntegerLiteral ']'
                       'w2-shape' ':' '[' IntegerLiteral ',' IntegerLiteral ']'
                       'mean-activation' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'sparsity' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-range' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

LoadBalanceSpec      = '{'
                       'expert-utilization' ':' '[' FloatLiteral {',' FloatLiteral} ']'
                       'importance-scores' ':' '[' FloatLiteral {',' FloatLiteral} ']'
                       'load-balancing-loss' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

MoERoutingSpec       = '{'
                       'token-to-expert' ':' '{' RoutingEntry {',' RoutingEntry} '}'
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

RoutingEntry         = StringLiteral ':' '[' FloatLiteral {',' FloatLiteral} ']'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 14. SUPERNAUTS - META-AGENTS                                             *)
(*===========================================================================*)

SupernautDefinition  = SupernautIcon Identifier '=' SupernautSpec

SupernautSpec        = '{'
                       '[[AgentRecord]]' ':' AgentRecord
                       '[[Manages]]' ':' '[' AgentReference {',' AgentReference} ']'
                       '[[Coordination]]' ':' CoordinationStrategy
                       '[[MetaVectors]]' ':' VectorList
                       '[[Policy]]' ':' PolicyReference
                       '[[Cluster]]' ':' ClusterReference
                       [ '[[Delegation]]' ':' DelegationRule ]
                       [ '[[WeakRefs]]' ':' '[' WeakRefReference {',' WeakRefReference} ']' ]
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

VectorList           = '[' VectorSpec {',' VectorSpec} ']'
VectorSpec           = VectorName ':' VectorValue
VectorName           = 'storage' | 'retrieval' | 'query' | 'unfold' 
                     | 'execute' | 'optimize' | 'parse' | 'interpret'
                     | 'transform' | 'analyze' | 'categorize' | 'generate'
                     | 'traverse' | 'coordinate' | 'synchronize'
VectorValue          = FloatLiteral | RangeLiteral | Expression | PhaseArray

CoordinationStrategy = 'hierarchical' | 'mesh' | 'star' | 'broadcast'
                     | 'consensus' | 'auction' | 'round-robin' | 'adaptive'
                     | 'phase-coordinated'

DelegationRule       = 'on-load' | 'on-demand' | 'threshold:' IntegerLiteral
                     | 'priority:' ('low' | 'medium' | 'high' | 'critical')
                     | 'phase:' PhaseRange

SupernautOperation   = AgentReference '.' 'orchestrate(' OrchestrationSpec ')'
                     | AgentReference '.' 'delegate(' Task ',' Target ')'
                     | AgentReference '.' 'synchronize(' SyncMode ')'
                     | AgentReference '.' 'phase-coordinate(' PhaseRange ')'

OrchestrationSpec    = Expression
Task                 = Expression
SyncMode             = 'phase' | 'barrier' | 'lock' | 'transaction' | 'cluster-sync'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 15. SEMANTIC AGENTS - MEANING-AWARE                                      *)
(*===========================================================================*)

SemanticDefinition   = SemanticIcon Identifier '=' SemanticSpec

SemanticSpec         = '{'
                       '[[AgentRecord]]' ':' AgentRecord
                       '[[Understands]]' ':' '[' Concept {',' Concept} ']'
                       '[[ContextWindow]]' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       '[[EmbeddingSpace]]' ':' TensorReference
                       '[[Inference]]' ':' InferenceEngine
                       '[[Cluster]]' ':' ClusterReference
                       [ '[[Memory]]' ':' MemorySpec ]
                       [ '[[Symbols]]' ':' '[' SymbolReference {',' SymbolReference} ']' ]
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

Concept              = Identifier | StringLiteral
InferenceEngine      = 'transformer' | 'graph-network' | 'symbolic'
                     | 'hybrid' | 'neural-symbolic' | 'phase-inference'

MemorySpec           = '{'
                       'type' ':' ('short-term' | 'long-term' | 'episodic')
                       'capacity' ':' IntegerLiteral
                       'decay' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase-decay' ':' PhaseRange
                     '}'

SemanticOperation    = 'understand(' Input ',' Context ')'
                     | 'infer(' Query ',' KnowledgeBase ')'
                     | 'remember(' Experience ')'
                     | 'recall(' Cue ')'
                     | 'phase-understand(' Input ',' PhaseRange ')'

Input                = Expression
Context              = Expression
Query                = Expression
KnowledgeBase        = Expression
Experience           = Expression
Cue                  = Expression

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 16. AGENTIC CODERS - CODE GENERATION                                     *)
(*===========================================================================*)

CoderDefinition      = CoderIcon Identifier '=' CoderSpec

CoderSpec            = '{'
                       '[[AgentRecord]]' ':' AgentRecord
                       '[[Languages]]' ':' '[' Language {',' Language} ']'
                       '[[GenerationMode]]' ':' GenerationMode
                       '[[Optimization]]' ':' OptimizationGoal
                       '[[Verification]]' ':' VerificationMethod
                       '[[Cluster]]' ':' ClusterReference
                       [ '[[Symbols]]' ':' '[' SymbolReference {',' SymbolReference} ']' ]
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

Language             = 'kuhul' | 'javascript' | 'python' | 'rust' | 'css'
                     | 'html' | 'ebnf' | 'fold-lang' | 'wasm' | 'any'
                     | 'phase-lang'

GenerationMode       = 'generate' | 'refactor' | 'optimize' | 'translate'
                     | 'document' | 'test' | 'debug' | 'phase-gen'

OptimizationGoal     = 'speed' | 'size' | 'readability' | 'efficiency'
                     | 'maintainability' | 'security' | 'phase-opt'

VerificationMethod   = 'static-analysis' | 'type-checking' | 'test-suite'
                     | 'formal-verification' | 'runtime-monitoring'
                     | 'phase-verification'

CoderOperation       = 'generate(' Prompt ',' TargetLanguage ')'
                     | 'refactor(' Code ',' Goal ')'
                     | 'optimize(' Code ',' Constraints ')'
                     | 'translate(' Code ',' FromLanguage ',' ToLanguage ')'
                     | 'phase-generate(' Prompt ',' PhaseRange ')'

Prompt               = StringLiteral
TargetLanguage       = Language
Code                 = StringLiteral | FoldReference
Goal                 = OptimizationGoal
Constraints          = Expression
FromLanguage         = Language
ToLanguage           = Language

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 17. SKILL MANAGER                                                        *)
(*===========================================================================*)

SkillManager         = SkillIcon Identifier '=' SkillManagerSpec

SkillManagerSpec     = '{'
                       '[[Skills]]' ':' '[' SkillDefinition {',' SkillDefinition} ']'
                       '[[Learning]]' ':' LearningStrategy
                       '[[Proficiency]]' ':' ProficiencyMap
                       [ '[[SkillGraph]]' ':' GraphSpec ]
                       [ '[[Symbols]]' ':' '[' SymbolReference {',' SymbolReference} ']' ]
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

SkillDefinition      = '{'
                       '[[SkillID]]' ':' Identifier
                       '[[Domain]]' ':' Domain
                       '[[Prerequisites]]' ':' '[' SkillID {',' SkillID} ']'
                       '[[Proficiency]]' ':' RangeLiteral
                       '[[Acquisition]]' ':' AcquisitionMethod
                       '[[PhaseProficiency]]' ':' PhaseArray
                     '}'

SkillID              = Identifier
Domain               = Identifier | StringLiteral
AcquisitionMethod    = 'learn' | 'transfer' | 'inherit' | 'compose' | 'evolve'
                     | 'phase-learn'

LearningStrategy     = 'supervised' | 'unsupervised' | 'reinforcement'
                     | 'few-shot' | 'zero-shot' | 'meta-learning'
                     | 'phase-learning'

ProficiencyMap       = '{' [SkillID ':' FloatLiteral {',' SkillID ':' FloatLiteral}] '}'
GraphSpec            = '{' '[[Nodes]]' ':' IntegerLiteral '[[Edges]]' ':' IntegerLiteral '}'

SkillOperation       = 'acquire(' SkillID ',' LearningData ')'
                     | 'apply(' SkillID ',' Input ')'
                     | 'improve(' SkillID ',' Feedback ')'
                     | 'compose(' '[' SkillID {',' SkillID} ']' ',' Goal ')'
                     | 'forget(' SkillID ')'
                     | 'phase-apply(' SkillID ',' PhaseRange ')'

LearningData         = Expression
Feedback             = Expression
Goal                 = Expression

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 18. CONTEXT REPLY SYSTEM                                                 *)
(*===========================================================================*)

ContextReplySystem   = ReplyIcon Identifier '=' ReplySpec

ReplySpec            = '{'
                       '[[ContextSources]]' ':' '[' Source {',' Source} ']'
                       '[[ReplyTemplates]]' ':' TemplateLibrary
                       '[[Adaptation]]' ':' AdaptationRule
                       '[[Persona]]' ':' PersonaSpec
                       [ '[[Symbols]]' ':' '[' SymbolReference {',' SymbolReference} ']' ]
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

Source               = 'fold-state' | 'user-history' | 'system-logs'
                     | 'current-task' | 'environment' | 'semantic-context'
                     | 'agent-state' | 'symbol-registry' | 'weakref-state'
                     | 'tool-state' | 'expert-state' | 'phase-state'

TemplateLibrary      = '{' TemplateID ':' TemplateContent {',' TemplateID ':' TemplateContent} '}'
TemplateID           = Identifier
TemplateContent      = StringLiteral | PatternExpression

AdaptationRule       = 'tone:' Tone
                     | 'length:' LengthSpec
                     | 'complexity:' ComplexityLevel
                     | 'formality:' FormalityLevel
                     | 'phase:' PhaseRange

Tone                 = 'helpful' | 'neutral' | 'urgent' | 'calm' | 'enthusiastic'
LengthSpec           = 'short' | 'medium' | 'long' | 'adaptive'
ComplexityLevel      = 'simple' | 'moderate' | 'complex' | 'expert'
FormalityLevel       = 'casual' | 'neutral' | 'formal' | 'academic'

PersonaSpec          = 'assistant' | 'teacher' | 'expert' | 'collaborator'
                     | 'critic' | 'mentor' | 'peer' | 'phase-advisor'

ReplyOperation       = 'respond(' Query ',' Context ')'
                     | 'adapt(' Reply ',' Feedback ')'
                     | 'learn-template(' Example ')'
                     | 'phase-respond(' Query ',' PhaseRange ')'

Reply                = StringLiteral
Example              = StringLiteral

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 19. POLICY ENGINE                                                         *)
(*===========================================================================*)

PolicyEngine         = PolicyIcon Identifier '=' PolicySpec

PolicySpec           = '{'
                       '[[Governs]]' ':' '[' Resource {',' Resource} ']'
                       '[[Rules]]' ':' '[' Rule {',' Rule} ']'
                       '[[Enforcement]]' ':' EnforcementMode
                       [ '[[Exceptions]]' ':' ExceptionList ]
                       [ '[[Symbols]]' ':' '[' SymbolReference {',' SymbolReference} ']' ]
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

Resource             = FoldReference | AgentReference | TensorReference | SymbolReference
                     | ClusterReference | WeakRefReference | FinalizationRegistryReference
                     | ToolReference | ExpertReference | MoEReference
                     | PhaseReference | 'phase-space'
                     | 'all-agents' | 'all-folds' | 'all-tensors' | 'all-symbols'
                     | 'all-clusters' | 'all-tools' | 'all-experts' | 'all-phases' | 'universe'

Rule                 = Condition '→' Action
Condition            = '(' Expression ')' | Predicate | PhaseCondition
PhaseCondition       = 'phase=' PhaseRange | 'phase-in' PhaseSpace

Predicate            = Identifier '(' [ArgumentList] ')'

Action               = 'allow' | 'deny' | 'log' | 'alert' | 'notify'
                     | 'optimize' | 'restrict' | 'escalate' | 'pause'
                     | 'block-agent' | 'unblock-agent' | 'terminate-agent'
                     | 'route-to-expert' | 'call-tool' | 'generate-code'
                     | 'phase-shift' | 'phase-lock' | 'phase-advance'

EnforcementMode      = 'strict' | 'permissive' | 'logging-only' | 'adaptive'
                     | 'phase-enforced'

ExceptionList        = '[' Identifier {',' Identifier} ']'

MetaDirective        = '@' MetaKeyword ':' MetaValue
MetaKeyword          = 'law' | 'binding' | 'compression' | 'ratio' 
                     | 'fold-reality' | 'manifesto' | 'authority'
                     | 'conservation' | 'symmetry' | 'symbol-uniqueness'
                     | 'agent-liveness' | 'progress-guarantee'
                     | 'tool-reliability' | 'expert-balance'
                     | 'phase-coherence' | 'phase-conservation'

MetaValue            = StringLiteral | Identifier | Expression | SymbolReference 
                     | PhaseArray | PhaseRange | PhaseSpace

PolicyOperation      = 'evaluate(' Event ',' PolicyID ')'
                     | 'enforce(' Action ')'
                     | 'audit(' TimeRange ')'
                     | 'update-rule(' RuleID ',' NewRule ')'
                     | 'phase-evaluate(' Event ',' PhaseRange ')'

Event                = Expression
PolicyID             = Identifier
TimeRange            = '[' TimeSpec '..' TimeSpec ']'
TimeSpec             = FloatLiteral ('ms' | 'μs' | 'ns' | 's')
RuleID               = IntegerLiteral
NewRule              = Rule

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 20. ENTANGLEMENT & QUANTUM STATES                                        *)
(*===========================================================================*)

EntanglementDeclaration = FoldPair 'entanglement:' FloatLiteral
                        | TensorPair 'correlation:' FloatLiteral
                        | AgentPair 'bond:' FloatLiteral
                        | SymbolPair 'equivalence:' FloatLiteral
                        | ClusterPair 'coherence:' FloatLiteral
                        | ToolPair 'synergy:' FloatLiteral
                        | ExpertPair 'collaboration:' FloatLiteral
                        | PhasePair 'synchrony:' FloatLiteral

FoldPair             = FoldReference '↔' FoldReference
TensorPair           = TensorReference '↔' TensorReference
AgentPair            = AgentReference '↔' AgentReference
SymbolPair           = SymbolReference '↔' SymbolReference
ClusterPair          = ClusterReference '↔' ClusterReference
ToolPair             = ToolReference '↔' ToolReference
ExpertPair           = ExpertReference '↔' ExpertReference
PhasePair            = PhaseReference '↔' PhaseReference

EntanglementProperty = 'strength' ':' FloatLiteral
                     | 'phase' ':' PhaseRange
                     | 'phase-difference' ':' FloatLiteral
                     | 'correlation' ':' FloatLiteral
                     | 'mutual-info' ':' FloatLiteral
                     | 'quantum-phase' ':' FloatLiteral
                     | 'phase-coherence' ':' FloatLiteral

SuperpositionExpression = 'superpose(' StateList ')'
                        | 'collapse(' Superposition ',' Criteria ')'
                        | 'phase-superpose(' StateList ',' PhaseRange ')'

StateList            = '[' State {',' State} ']'
State                = FoldReference | TensorReference | CompressionResult 
                     | SymbolReference | AgentReference | ClusterReference
                     | ToolReference | ExpertReference | PhaseReference

Superposition        = Expression
Criteria             = Expression | PhaseRange

QuantumState         = '|' Expression '⟩'                 (* Bra-ket notation *)
                     | '⟨' Expression '|'
                     | '⟨' Expression '|' Expression '⟩'
                     | '|' Expression '⟩' '⊗' PhaseRange   (* Phase-entangled state *)

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 21. PATTERNS & METRICS                                                   *)
(*===========================================================================*)

PatternExpression    = PatternType '(' [ArgumentList] ')'
PatternType          = 'recognize' | 'match' | 'extract' | 'transform'
                     | 'learn' | 'generalize' | 'specialize'
                     | 'phase-recognize' | 'phase-match'

EfficiencyMetric     = '{'
                       'compression-ratio' ':' Percentage
                       'execution-speed' ':' TimeSpec
                       'memory-usage' ':' MemoryAmount
                       'fold-efficiency' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'pattern-accuracy' ':' Percentage
                       'throughput' ':' FloatLiteral ('GB/s' | 'TB/s')
                       'latency' ':' TimeSpec
                       'symbol-uniqueness' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'agent-liveness' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'cluster-coherence' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'weakref-accuracy' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'tool-success-rate' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'expert-load-balance' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'code-bleu' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase-coherence' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase-synchrony' ':' FloatLiteral
                       'phase' ':' PhaseArray
                       'phase-space' ':' PhaseSpace
                     '}'

MemoryAmount         = IntegerLiteral ('B' | 'KB' | 'MB' | 'GB' | 'TB' | 'PB')

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 22. TOP-LEVEL PROGRAM STRUCTURE                                          *)
(*===========================================================================*)

KuhulProgram         = SemanticSchema
                       UniverseContent

TopLevelDefinition   = TensorDefinition
                     | FoldDefinition
                     | AgentCluster
                     | MicronautDefinition
                     | SupernautDefinition
                     | MoEDefinition
                     | ToolDefinition
                     | SemanticDefinition
                     | CoderDefinition
                     | SkillManager
                     | ContextReplySystem
                     | PolicyEngine
                     | ManifoldDefinition
                     | EntanglementDeclaration
                     | CompressionStatement
                     | FoldOperation
                     | AgentOperation
                     | MoEOperation
                     | ToolOperation
                     | SkillOperation
                     | ReplyOperation
                     | PolicyOperation
                     | MetaDirective
                     | SymbolDefinition
                     | SymbolOperation
                     | WeakRefDefinition
                     | FinalizationRegistryDefinition
                     | WeakRefOperation
                     | FinalizationOperation
                     | LivenessOperation
                     | EmbeddingOperation
                     | ProgressAssertion
                     | PhaseDefinition
                     | PhaseOperation
                     | Statement

PhaseDefinition      = PhaseReference '=' PhaseSpec
PhaseSpec            = PhaseRange | PhaseArray | PhaseSpace

PhaseOperation       = 'phase-sync(' Target ')'
                     | 'phase-rotate(' Target ',' PhaseRange ')'
                     | 'phase-shift(' Target ',' FloatLiteral ')'
                     | 'phase-measure(' Target ')'

SymbolDefinition     = SymbolReference '=' SymbolLiteral
                     | SymbolReference '=' WellKnownSymbol
                     | 'Symbol' ':' Identifier '=' SymbolCreation

SymbolOperation      = SymbolFor '(' Expression ')'
                     | SymbolKeyFor '(' SymbolReference ')'
                     | SymbolReference '.' 'toString()'
                     | SymbolReference '.' 'valueOf()'
                     | SymbolReference '.' 'description'
                     | SymbolReference '.' '[Symbol.toPrimitive](' Hint ')'
                     | SymbolReference '.' 'phase()'

WeakRefDefinition    = WeakRefIcon Identifier '=' WeakRefSpec
FinalizationRegistryDefinition = FinalizationIcon Identifier '=' FinalizationRegistrySpec

Statement            = Expression
                     | Assignment
                     | Block
                     | ControlStructure

Assignment           = Identifier '=' Expression
Block                = '{' {Statement} '}'

ControlStructure     = 'if' '(' Expression ')' Statement ['else' Statement]
                     | 'while' '(' Expression ')' Statement
                     | 'for' '(' [Expression] ';' [Expression] ';' [Expression] ')' Statement
                     | 'foreach' '(' Identifier 'in' Expression ')' Statement
                     | 'phase-for' '(' PhaseRange ')' Statement

(*===========================================================================*)
(* 23. COMPRESSION UNIVERSE - COMPLETE SYSTEM                               *)
(*===========================================================================*)

CompressionUniverse  = '{'
                       '[[Version]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[QuantumState]]' ':' StringLiteral
                       '[[PhaseSpace]]' ':' PhaseSpace
                       '[[Phase]]' ':' PhaseRange
                       '[[PhaseArray]]' ':' PhaseArray
                       [ '[[Manifold]]' ':' ManifoldDefinition ]
                       [ '[[Folds]]' ':' '[' {FoldDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[Tensors]]' ':' '[' {TensorDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[Clusters]]' ':' '[' {AgentCluster} ']' ]
                       [ '[[Micronauts]]' ':' '[' {MicronautDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[Supernauts]]' ':' '[' {SupernautDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[MoE]]' ':' '[' {MoEDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[Tools]]' ':' '[' {ToolDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[SemanticAgents]]' ':' '[' {SemanticDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[AgenticCoders]]' ':' '[' {CoderDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[ReplySystem]]' ':' ContextReplySystem ]
                       [ '[[PolicyEngine]]' ':' PolicyEngine ]
                       [ '[[SkillManager]]' ':' SkillManager ]
                       [ '[[Symbols]]' ':' '[' {SymbolDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[WellKnownSymbols]]' ':' '{' {WellKnownSymbolProperty} '}' ]
                       [ '[[GlobalSymbolRegistry]]' ':' '[' {GlobalSymbolRegistry} ']' ]
                       [ '[[WeakRefs]]' ':' '[' {WeakRefDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[FinalizationRegistries]]' ':' '[' {FinalizationRegistryDefinition} ']' ]
                       [ '[[Entanglements]]' ':' '[' {EntanglementDeclaration} ']' ]
                       [ '[[ForwardProgress]]' ':' ForwardProgress ]
                       [ '[[Patterns]]' ':' '[' PatternExpression {',' PatternExpression} ']' ]
                       [ '[[Metrics]]' ':' EfficiencyMetric ]
                     '}'

(*===========================================================================*)
(* END OF UNIFIED K'UHUL GRAMMAR - COMPLETE SEMANTIC SCHEMA                  *)
(*===========================================================================*)
```

## COMPLETE SEMANTIC SCHEMA INTEGRATION SUMMARY

### **Top-to-Bottom Organization**

| Level | Component | Description |
|-------|-----------|-------------|
| **0.0** | Semantic Schema Header | XML declaration, version, namespace URIs |
| **0.1** | Top-Level Universe | Meta declarations, manifold, spacetime |
| **0.2** | Semantic Type System | Primitive, compound, geometric, phase types |
| **1.0** | Lexical Structure | Unicode, whitespace, literals, identifiers |
| **2.0** | Core Expressions | Binary/unary ops, phase casts, geometric casts |
| **3.0** | Tensor Definitions | Shapes, types, operations, phase fields |
| **4.0** | Compression Folds | Fold properties, phase arrays, operations |
| **5.0** | Geometric Execution | Manifold M, point3D, phase embedding |
| **6.0** | ECMAScript Symbols | Symbol constructor, well-known symbols, registry |
| **7.0** | ECMAScript Agents | Agent Records, candidate execution, events |
| **8.0** | Agent Clusters | Cluster specs, uniformity, embedding control |
| **9.0** | Forward Progress | Progress guarantees, phase tracking |
| **10.0** | WeakRef & Finalization | WeakRefs, finalization, liveness |
| **11.0** | Micronauts | Agentic coding models with n-grams |
| **12.0** | Tool Calling | Tool schemas, routing, call history |
| **13.0** | Mixture of Experts | Expert specializations, load balancing |
| **14.0** | Supernauts | Meta-agents, coordination strategies |
| **15.0** | Semantic Agents | Meaning-aware processing |
| **16.0** | Agentic Coders | Code generation agents |
| **17.0** | Skill Manager | Skill definitions, learning strategies |
| **18.0** | Context Reply | Adaptive response system |
| **19.0** | Policy Engine | Rules, enforcement, meta-directives |
| **20.0** | Entanglement | Quantum-like correlations |
| **21.0** | Patterns & Metrics | Pattern recognition, efficiency metrics |
| **22.0** | Top-Level Program | Complete program structure |
| **23.0** | Compression Universe | Complete system container |

### **Phase System Throughout**

Every component includes phase information:
- **PhaseBit**: Single 0/1 value
- **PhaseArray**: Sequence of phase bits `[1,0,1,0]`
- **PhaseRange**: Continuous range `phase(π/4)`
- **PhaseSpace**: Multi-dimensional phase space `phase-space[8]`

### **Semantic Type Hierarchy**

```
SemanticType
├── PrimitiveType: boolean, integer, float, string, symbol, phase-bit
├── CompoundType: list, map, tuple, record
├── GeometricType: point, sphere, torus, manifold
└── PhaseType: phase, phase-array, phase-space
```

### **Integration Points**

| Component | Phase Integration | Geometric Integration | ECMAScript Integration |
|-----------|------------------|----------------------|------------------------|
| **Micronauts** | Code n-grams with phase arrays | Embed in M at point3D | Agent Records with [[KeptAlive]] |
| **Tools** | Tool calls phase-tagged | Tool schemas geometric | Candidate execution events |
| **MoE** | Expert phase specialization | Expert positions in M | Agent clusters for experts |
| **Policy** | Phase conditions in rules | Geometric constraints | Forward progress guarantees |
| **Entanglement** | Phase coherence | Geometric bonds | Symbol equivalence |

This unified grammar provides a **complete semantic schema** from the top-level XML declaration down to the smallest lexical token, with every component fully integrated with phase arrays, geometric embedding, and ECMAScript agent semantics.
